works.description:
The just released Snowbreeze 2.4 can now jailbreak iPhone, iPad and iPod Touch devices running on iOS 4.3.1. Sn0wbreeze 2.4 also makes Ultrasn0w, the tool to make the device free of official carriers, compatible with iOS 4.3.1 on unlockable basebands.

As you know Sn0wbreeze is Windows OS based tool but if you are a Mac user you can use PwnageTool and PwnageTool bundles to jailbreak your device. The detailed tutorial for Mac OS users is posted here.
